": "markdown", "html": "<p>This issue is related with the interactive marker after releasing the button in scale mode. The model is always scaled but the interactive marker is not always scaled in the same proportion. Try inserting a box, enlarge it, and then, reduce its size to its original dimension to see this effect. You'll notice that the interactive marker does not have the original size.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Ian Chen", "uuid": "{eaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5/1e4adcdf-1946-4280-9aea-eb5f15a7f912/128"}}, "nickname": "Ian Chen", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-10-16T22:55:19.847672+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:44:39.116763+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 897}